<note n="0194002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0194002">ālu, Kaḷamba, biḷalī, takkaḷa, kola, bhallātaka, bella 以上均為球根之植物。</note>
<note n="0194003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0194003">Sumekhali（善帶）。</note>
<note n="0195001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0195001">Reṇu（花粉）。</note>
<note n="0196001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0196001">Nivāsaka（住）。此係就阿薩努帕塔耶迦長老而言。</note>
</p>
